{
  "stem": "7282.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was the most-- and on the street where we lived, I had some more kids who used to play, like, a Katz again, Mojshe Katz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We used to go in the same-- in the same class and-- doing a lecture, Polish or whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But-- like boys in this age, well, we didn't set-- we didn't sit still.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know how it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when the teacher used to come into the classroom, I used to say, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This means, one Katz stays on the knees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The other one goes out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the children remains in the class.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What-- so that was, I mean-- and when I went to cheder, there, I had other kids what I used to-- I used to play with them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the most were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There wasn't non-Jewish because the most, it was the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Jewish neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In school, what, I mean, it was a mix.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, it was a public school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- there are Polish, Russian, Ukrainian, all kinds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there, they used to give us a terrible-- they used to call us 'Zyd' and all kinds of names.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the, the-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The teachers, I, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One teacher, I do remember what-- I mean, he was a teacher of music.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when he used to come into the school, he used to say, like, I mean, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 'Chaim,' or 'Moishe'-- we used to-- Jewish pronounce 'chhha.' He used to, like, he used to call on somebody, 'Chhhaim.' He used to pronounce the 'chhha'-- what.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He gave you a little bit--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And another teacher I remember-- it was a math teacher.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- I think he was a German guy, what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he knew Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
